{"tid":1593593,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【十一行動】全香港同一時間唱《願榮光歸香港》","createTime":"2019-09-25T06:46:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T12:32:09.000Z","uid":70493,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6d9422107201b8aaf50e37a63f9a1451f46dbb24","tid":1593593,"uid":70493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T06:46:38.000Z","msg":"我尋晚發夢，夢見全香港同一時間百萬人一齊唱《願榮光歸香港》。<br />\n<br />\n大家諗吓，十月一號政府一定會升國旗，唱中國國歌。<br />\n我地有冇可能全香港人同一時間一齊唱《願榮光歸香港》？<br />\n如果做得到，就會上倒國際頭條，<br />\nHong Kong is not China! <br />\n<br />\n無論係喺街上遊行緊嘅人，<br />\n定係喺屋企，<br />\n有冇可能定一個時間，全世界一齊唱？<br />\n甚至連同海外香港人？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n甚至，我地可唔可能定一個地點，<br />\n組織一個街上嘅快閃管弦樂團同合唱團？<br />\n例如維園，出現幾萬人嘅樂團同合唱團，有冇可能？<br />\n而且要有 camera 影住，全世界直播。<br />\n我希望我唔係發夢！<br />\n<br />\n支持嘅請推 post，同埋討論吓點樣組織呢件事。<br />\n我係廢中，唔多識用 Telegram，如果有人識得點樣去設立行動組，<br />\n請諗諗辦法。"},{"pid":"a6e734fde09b9abaea5cda9cf2dbaef059448bf3","tid":1593593,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T06:48:07.000Z","msg":"大家要記住呀！！！！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">929反赤納粹行動</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全球呀！</span></strong></span><br />\n我地唔可以輸比世界上任何一個地區，我地幾咁憎赤納粹<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要求正虎黑警交代831，新屋嶺！要求了解被捕義士情況！求真相求解釋！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲有仲有，唔好唔記得今個月大家有咩要做呀！！！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JQzoLGj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJQzoLGj.jpg&h=602349be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HYuoLGk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHYuoLGk.jpg&h=6570c191&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有仲有仲有！930大罷工，國㷫前夕點少得以死城幫中共㷫燭呀？？？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5mJwHid.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5mJwHid.png&h=6ac8ea34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n推推推推推，p牌仔開唔到post唯有洗爆你地留言！"},{"pid":"9bca969e0db49b137a6cb4c7acf8477fa1d0c917","tid":1593593,"uid":70493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T06:49:13.000Z","msg":"乜嘢時間最好？<br />\n1. 同升旗禮同一時間，一大朝早？<br />\n2. 遊行期間，例如下午某個鐘？<br />\n<br />\n快閃樂隊，地點邊度好？<br />\n1. 維園？<br />\n2. 政總外?"},{"pid":"54eaeb53a7ff91f64c17b324ecc70e25477ad49d","tid":1593593,"uid":70493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T06:49:43.000Z","msg":"有冇人支持？<br />\n支持請推 post"},{"pid":"688a198d38978b6d71cf4472d1518d9bac63fbd5","tid":1593593,"uid":70493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T06:49:57.000Z","msg":"自推十連 <br />\n1"},{"pid":"042cb0a0f165833dbe4bbcab7e7248b525d38472","tid":1593593,"uid":70493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T06:50:07.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"65506c3e3afa6fbb738fe254da39d78ccd5b5df2","tid":1593593,"uid":70493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T06:50:20.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"14bdd3ca8727491435d6507420e109fa6a98961b","tid":1593593,"uid":70493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T06:50:35.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"c0796967c70281be503efa3b2700b55ec2caeed7","tid":1593593,"uid":70493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T06:50:50.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"8b3537d5d882fea2a1c88ef4c95240894e35783c","tid":1593593,"uid":70493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T06:51:14.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"a7426c04d941576b47969014bb7332cf0566a09b","tid":1593593,"uid":70493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T06:51:47.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"767cfaeb58e2a4c8916fb9550c09cc34220